---
title: Miso Aubergine with garlic rice and pickled veg
description: Miso is a Japanese ingredient that's the ultimate instiller of umami flavour. In this recipe, it coats soft and golden aubergine along with toasted sesame seeds for a symphony of Asian flavours that work beautifully together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R07_W41_IE_IEVV17426-2_Main_high-e67f9c85.jpg
